version_description: Minor bugs fixed as our QA team is obsessed with perfectionism. :)
- Performance improved and bugs fixed. So, how about going out and taking more beautiful pics with our supercharged app, eh?

Thank you for staying with us! We are updating the app regularly to make it even better.
Here’s what’s new:
• Bug fixes and performance improvements.

Heads up, selfie lovers!
A new update of Selfish has finally arrived. Join now and try new features!
– Updated User Interface (UI): provides a more modern and streamlined user experience
– Brand-new list of effects for new users
– Updated License Agreement compliant with latest data laws.

We’ve also fixed a few minor bugs to make the app run smoothly.
Did we miss something? Come on! Tell us what you think of this update in the comments section.
